README for Tie::Filehandle::Preempt::Stdin

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

If you are on a Windows box you should use 'nmake' rather than 'make'.

DEPENDENCIES

None.

